# PokerPro Analytics

A comprehensive web-based poker analysis platform that provides real-time mathematical analysis, strategic insights, and bankroll management tools for poker players of all skill levels.

## Overview

PokerPro Analytics transforms poker decision-making from intuition-based to mathematically-driven analysis. It calculates the precise probability of winning any poker hand, determines optimal betting strategies, and provides professional-level insights that help players make better decisions at the table.

## Features

### Hand Equity Analysis
- Calculate exact winning probabilities for any two-card starting hand
- Support for 1-9 opponents using Monte Carlo simulations
- Position-aware recommendations (UTG, MP, CO, BTN, SB, BB)
- Real-time equity calculations with confidence intervals
- GTO frequency recommendations for optimal play

### Bankroll Management
- Professional risk assessment using Kelly Criterion principles
- Risk of ruin calculations with realistic percentages
- Buy-in ratio analysis and recommendations
- Conservative, moderate, and aggressive bankroll strategies
- Growth projections based on win rates and variance

### Tournament Strategy Analysis
- M-ratio calculations for tournament play
- ICM (Independent Chip Model) pressure analysis
- Stage-specific strategy recommendations
- Blind level progression tracking
- Push-fold strategy optimization

### Game Theory Optimal (GTO) Solver
- Optimal betting frequencies for any scenario
- Preflop and postflop strategy recommendations
- Stack-to-pot ratio considerations
- Exploitability analysis
- Nash equilibrium calculations

### Session Tracking
- Comprehensive session logging
- Profit/loss tracking with hourly rates
- Performance analytics and trend analysis
- Game type categorization
- Historical data visualization

